[normal]Q3 [bold]&#xa0; 
[normal]Mr Lilley:[bold] What empirical evidence would it take to convince you that the world’s temperature sensitivity to increases in carbon dioxide is at the bottom of the level in the IPCC report and
[normal],
[normal] therefore
[normal],
